{"id": 62477, "date": "2025-11-28T04:00:27", "date_gmt": "2025-11-28T12:00:27", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=62477"}, "modified": "2026-07-01T11:53:52", "modified_gmt": "2026-07-01T18:53:52", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-november-28-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/11/28/kingdom-of-days-november-28-2/", "title": {"rendered": "November 28"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1971: </strong>The Bruce Springsteen Band is in residence at the Student Prince in Asbury Park.</p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>Bruce holds a recording session at The Record Plant in New York City, where he and the band work on &#8220;Racing in the Street.&#8221;</p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band bring the Darkness Tour to the Dane County Memorial Coliseum in Madison, Wisconsin.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/18_SB3a9Jbo?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"14325\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/47544237051_e03acb5d43_o/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/47544237051_e03acb5d43_o.jpg?fit=840%2C305&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"840,305\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Picasa&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1335106938&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"47544237051_e03acb5d43_o\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/47544237051_e03acb5d43_o.jpg?fit=758%2C275&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14325 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/47544237051_e03acb5d43_o.jpg?resize=758%2C275&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/47544237051_e03acb5d43_o.jpg?w=840&amp;ssl=1 840w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/47544237051_e03acb5d43_o.jpg?resize=300%2C109&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/47544237051_e03acb5d43_o.jpg?resize=768%2C279&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></strong></p>\n<p><strong>1980:\u00a0</strong>On Black Friday, Bruce and the band play their second of two nights at Madison Square Garden in New York City. This show features a very unusual &#8220;Ramrod&#8221;/&#8221;Living on the Edge of the World&#8221; (the latter of which hadn&#8217;t even been released) mashup, as well as the tour premiere of &#8220;4th of July, Asbury Park (Sandy).&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4HUThNRDG0E?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLJTyL9twk3zA4JUhmcl5oNlOk1Mn6t5dg\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>The first leg of the Reunion Tour enters its last stand when Bruce and the E Street Band play their first of two nights at the Target Center in Minneapolis. The holidays must be approaching&#8211;Bruce closes the show with the tour premiere of &#8220;Santa Claus is Comin&#8217; to Town.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WGTS8ii7nrU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"22869\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1999-11-28/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1999-11-28.png?fit=1558%2C1752&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1558,1752\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1999-11-28\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1999-11-28.png?fit=758%2C852&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-22869 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1999-11-28.png?resize=758%2C852&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"852\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1999-11-28.png?w=1558&amp;ssl=1 1558w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1999-11-28.png?resize=267%2C300&amp;ssl=1 267w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1999-11-28.png?resize=911%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 911w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1999-11-28.png?resize=768%2C864&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1999-11-28.png?resize=1366%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1366w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2007:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the band play a fantastic Magic show in Milan to an Italian crowd that&#8217;s on fire.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/piMODx-_KYk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/s_-qAkqj8D8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/6RqWMY69A4I?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/D5hgaIMDNpI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZakunwBioKo?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2008:\u00a0</strong>Bruce releases &#8220;My Lucky Day,&#8221; the second single from his upcoming album,\u00a0<em>Working on a Dream</em>.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/gO7vFDfhDHw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2012:\u00a0</strong>Bruce continues shaking up the Wrecking Ball set list at the Rose Garden in Portland, opening with &#8220;Land of Hope and Dreams,&#8221; and featuring rare outings for &#8220;Loose Ends,&#8221; &#8220;Seeds,&#8221; and &#8220;Drive All Night.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Zq_7TStsvg0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/k8ZlKq7V9Sg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xo6m2n2Gr0s?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2016:\u00a0</strong>Bruce resumes his promotional book tour, making an appearance at Books-a-Million in Chicago.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/tyxMb8BCcUY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/uKGsQY00vnc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2018: </strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway</em> begins the final leg of its theatrical run (minus Patti, who is absent tonight). In attendance: Patterson Hood of the Drive-By Truckers.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"14326\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2018-11-28/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2018-11-28.jpg?fit=422%2C422&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"422,422\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2018-11-28\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2018-11-28.jpg?fit=422%2C422&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14326 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2018-11-28.jpg?resize=422%2C422&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"422\" height=\"422\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2018-11-28.jpg?w=422&amp;ssl=1 422w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2018-11-28.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2018-11-28.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2018-11-28.jpg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 422px) 100vw, 422px\" /></p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Santa comes out in &#8217;99, an intense Magic show in Milan, and a unique Ramrod/Living on the Edge of the World mash-up&#8211;all and more from this date.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 70278, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_feature_clip_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false}, "categories": [2], "tags": [1627, 162, 91, 508, 1596, 199, 957, 360, 661, 1591, 630, 2544, 560, 680, 367, 128, 1008, 626, 273, 1324, 778, 445], "class_list": ["post-62477", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-kingdom-of-days", "tag-born-to-run-book", "tag-bruce-springsteen-band", "tag-chicago", "tag-darkness-tour", "tag-living-on-the-edge-of-the-world", "tag-madison", "tag-madison-square-garden", "tag-magic-tour", "tag-milan", "tag-minneapolis", "tag-new-york-city", "tag-patterson-hood", "tag-portland", "tag-ramrod", "tag-reunion-tour", "tag-river-tour", "tag-santa-claus-is-comin-to-town", "tag-seeds", "tag-springsteen-on-broadway", "tag-streets-of-fire", "tag-student-prince", "tag-wrecking-ball-tour"], "aioseo_notices": [], "aioseo_head": "\n\t\t<!-- All in One SEO 4.9.9 - aio